<p id="O6ne3c">I spent a lot of time testing both the <a href="https://www.theverge.com/23484927/amazon-kindle-scribe-e-reader-notetaking-pen-review">Kindle Scribe</a> and the Kobo Elipsa 2E, and ultimately <a href="https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers">Kobo’s is my favorite...</a></p>
